  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your to-do list just got electrifying.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charge devices, water plants, or tidy up—but this house and garden are packed with peril . Sparks, faulty cords, and sneaky traps lurk in every corner. Will you survive?<br><br><strong>Pick Your Playstyle:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adventure Mode:</strong> Roam freely, dodge hazards, and enjoy the journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrun Mode:</strong> Compete on leaderboards for the fastest cleanup!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2635290/extras/e34017d4198ee3478721f3c90de032e8.poster.avif?t=1746011903\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2635290/extras/e34017d4198ee3478721f3c90de032e8.webm?t=1746011903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2635290/extras/e34017d4198ee3478721f3c90de032e8.mp4?t=1746011903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why Play?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For Everyone:</strong> Tackle chores casually or race for the high score—your choice!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Electrifying Hazards:</strong> Dodge rogue appliances, frayed wires, and wet zones—all while keeping your sanity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hidden Risks in Every Corner:</strong> Explore every room and yard in a charming, danger-filled world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>“This isn’t a chore—it’s an obstacle course!”</i></strong><br>Dive in and turn mundane tasks into electrifying adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2635290/extras/03705c90426c93ab6a8ae6f7c99d4238.poster.avif?t=1746011903\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2635290/extras/03705c90426c93ab6a8ae6f7c99d4238.webm?t=1746011903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2635290/extras/03705c90426c93ab6a8ae6f7c99d4238.mp4?t=1746011903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
